          "text": [
            "when the event matches <a href='javascript:editParameter(\"2\", \"1\")' class='dynamic'>( \tLOWER(&quot;Parent Process Full Full Name&quot;) == 'hh.exe' \tAND  \tLOWER(&quot;Process Full Full Name&quot;) IN ('cmd.exe','powershell.exe','pwsh.exe','wscript.exe','cscript.exe','regsvr32.exe','wmic.exe','rundll32.exe','mshta.exe','certutil.exe','certreq.exe','msbuild.exe','installutil.exe','schtasks.exe','msiexec.exe') ) OR ( \tLOWER(&quot;Process Full Full Name&quot;) == 'hh.exe' \tAND  \t( \t\tLOWER(&quot;Command&quot;) LIKE '%.application%' \t\tOR LOWER(&quot;Command&quot;) LIKE '%\\downloads\\%' \t\tOR LOWER(&quot;Command&quot;) LIKE '%\\content.outlook\\%' \t\tOR LOWER(&quot;Command&quot;) LIKE '%\\appdata\\local\\temp\\%' \t) )</a> AQL filter query"
